==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Whaler
<hw>Whal"er</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who whales, or beats; a big,
strong fellow; hence, anything of great or unusual size.</def>
<mark>[Colloq. U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Whaling</ent>⟦br⟧
